{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"5":{"eng-name":"Prayer (Kitab Al-Salat): Voluntary Prayers","ara-name":"كتاب التطوع"}},"section_detail":{"5":{"hadithnumber_first":1250,"hadithnumber_last":1370,"arabicnumber_first":1250,"arabicnumber_last":1370}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1344,"arabicnumber":1344,"text":"। সাঈদ (রহঃ) হতে পূর্বোক্ত হাদীসের অনুরূপ বর্ণিত। ‘আয়িশাহ্ (রাঃ) বলেন, তিনি এমনভাবে সালাম ফিরাতেন যে, আমরা শুনতে পেতাম। যেমনটি রয়েছে ইয়াহইয়া ইবনু সাঈদ এর বর্ণনায়।[1] সহীহ।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":5,"hadith":95},"chapter":{"id":27,"ara-name":"باب فِي صَلاَةِ اللَّيْلِ","eng-name":"On The Night Prayer","isFirstHadith":false}}]}